changelist-link-to-tabs.text:
!! $:/plugins/wikilabs/link-to-tabs

解决问题：水平标签页选中 tab 出现下划线

* $:/plugins/wikilabs/link-to-tabs/styles
* 将其中对应样式修改为：

```css
.wltc-link-to-tab {
  display: {{$:/plugins/wikilabs/link-to-tabs/config!!show-all-links}};
  position: relative;
  top: -0.6em;
  left: -0.8em;
  opacity: {{$:/plugins/wikilabs/link-to-tabs/config!!initial-opacity}};
  margin-right: -1em;
}

.wltc-link-to-tab svg{
  width: 0.97em;
  height: 0.97em;
}
```

